fection of the heart from some good to be attained:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA: [in both of which are further explanations, for which see 1:]) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_imolapN","text_ar":"اـِمْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amalN","text_ar":"اَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"page_break","n":100},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA_omiylN","text_ar":"تَاـْمِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Lh, M, K;) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a manner of hoping"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expecting;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for J adds,] and it is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jilosapN","text_ar":"جِلْسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rikobapN","text_ar":"رِكْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muw^am~alN","text_ar":"مُوَمَّلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", likewise, signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_amalN","text_ar":"اـَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^malN","text_ar":"امَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_amolN","text_ar":"اـَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amolN","text_ar":"اَمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=malN","text_ar":"ا=مَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, * K, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAba saEoyuhu waA^amaluhu","text_ar":"خَابَ سَعْيُهُ وَاَمَلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His labour, and his hope,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expectation, were disappointed, frustrated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"balked"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xyb","text_ar":"خيب"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^aTowala A_amolatahu","text_ar":"مَا اَطْوَلَ اـَمْلَتَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How far-reaching is his hope,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expectation!"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, * S, M, K:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his manner of hoping"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expecting!"},{"kind":"text","text":"] from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amalu","text_ar":"الاَمَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) ―         -b2-  Also, the first,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An object of hope."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel in xviii. 44.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Msb","K","IJ","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}